<th colspan="2" style="text-align: center;"><big class="fn summary">Charles Ponzi</big></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" align="center">
<div class="center">
<div class="floatnone"><a href="/wiki/File:21rampell.xlarge1.jpg" class="image" title="21rampell.xlarge1.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/a/aa/21rampell.xlarge1.jpg/300px-21rampell.xlarge1.jpg" width="300" height="180" border="0" /></a></div>
